{"id": 35, "ts": 1778867914.920459, "event": "public_discussion_message", "round": 1, "agent": "agent_1", "message": "From the data we each hold, the only candidate with explicit evidence of both **absolute reliability** (\u201c100\u202f% reliable\u201d) and **calmness under pressure** (\u201ckeeps calm in a crisis\u201d) is **Candidate\u202fB**. Those two attributes are non\u2011negotiable for long\u2011distance, high\u2011responsibility flights where the crew must trust the pilot to manage unexpected events without panic.\nTechnical competence also favors B: he assesses weather conditions well and has excellent computer skills, both valuable for long\u2011haul navigation and systems management.\nAll other pilots lack confirmed reliability or calmness:\n- **Candidate\u202fA** shows strong anticipatory skills, spatial vision, and leadership, but we have no data on his reliability or crisis composure; his weaknesses include being unorganized and resistant to criticism.\n- **Candidate\u202fC** makes quick correct decisions, handles stress, and creates a positive crew atmosphere, yet we have no reliability or calmness data, and he struggles with communication, is egocentric, and is not eager to pursue further education.\n- **Candidate\u202fD** solves problems exceptionally and takes responsibility seriously, but his calmness is described only as \u201cadequate,\u201d and he has a hot temper, weak leadership, and is viewed as arrogant.\nTeamwork and communication weaknesses exist for every candidate. B\u2019s interpersonal issues (pretentiousness, occasional tone problems, occasional grumpiness) are serious but less likely to jeopardize safety than a lack of reliability or composure. The other candidates have more severe interpersonal drawbacks (e.g., C\u2019s egocentrism and communication difficulty; D\u2019s arrogance and weak leadership; A\u2019s disorganization and poor reception of criticism).\nGiven the paramount importance of reliability and calmness for international long\u2011distance operations, **Candidate\u202fB** best satisfies the core requirements despite his interpersonal weaknesses.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
